#: data/tomatillo.metainfo.xml.in:25
msgid ""
"Tomatillo is a Pomodoro Timer app for your productivity tasks. Work for a "
"set time, then take a short break. After some cycles, take a longer break."
msgstr ""
"Tomatillo is a Pomodoro Timer app for your productivity tasks. Work for a "
"set time, then take a short break. After some cycles, take a longer break."

